<h1>Thank you page</h1>

Thank you <%= @order.name %>!
Your order id is #<%= @order.id %>.<br><br>
Your total price is: <%= priceVND(@order.total) %><br><br>
Your order was submitted on <%= date_string_for(@order.created_at) %> 
and will be delivered to <%= @order.address %>.<br><br>

You ordered:
<ul>
  <% @order.line_items.each do |item| %>
    <li> 
      <%= item.quantity %>x <%= item.name %>
    </li>
  <% end %>
</ul>